languages.text: "Я не могу предсказывать будущее — в любом деле есть шанс дурного исхода. Выбери я иной путь, префект нашла бы изъяны и в нем".
"I cannot predict the future — a poor outcome is a possibility in every case. If I had chosen a different path, the prefect still would have found fault with it."
languages.original_text: "Я не могу предсказывать будущее — в любом деле есть шанс дурного исхода. Выбери я иной путь, префект нашла бы изъяны и в нем".

languages.text: "Ich kann nicht in die Zukunft sehen ... ein unerfreuliches Ende ist immer möglich. Hätte ich einen anderen Weg gewählt, hätte die Präfektin trotzdem einen Fehler gefunden."
languages.original_text: "I cannot predict the future — a poor outcome is a possibility in every case. If I had chosen a different path, the prefect still would have found fault with it."

languages.text: « Je ne peux pas prédire l'avenir. Une issue défavorable n'est jamais à exclure. Si j'avais choisi une voie différente, la préfète y aurait tout de même trouvé à redire. »
languages.original_text: "I cannot predict the future — a poor outcome is a possibility in every case. If I had chosen a different path, the prefect still would have found fault with it."

languages.text: “我没办法未卜先知。无论是什么样的决定，都可能会导致糟糕的结果。就算我当时选择了其他方案，行政官肯定还是会挑我的刺。”
languages.original_text: "I cannot predict the future — a poor outcome is a possibility in every case. If I had chosen a different path, the prefect still would have found fault with it."

languages.text: «No puedo predecir el futuro; los resultados desfavorables siempre son una posibilidad. De haber elegido otro camino, la prefecta habría encontrado fallos en él también».
languages.original_text: "I cannot predict the future — a poor outcome is a possibility in every case. If I had chosen a different path, the prefect still would have found fault with it."

languages.text: 「未来を予測することはできない。どんな選択にも悪い結果の可能性はある。別の道を選んでいたとしても、総監はやはり難癖をつけていただろう」

languages.text: "Geleceği görme yeteneğim yok... Yapılan her hareketin kötü sonuçlar doğurması mümkün. Farklı bir yol seçseydim Prefekt ne yapar eder, onda da bir kusur bulurdu."
